Subclasses of Parameter in sim
 class ColorParameter
          ColorParameter extends Parameter to implement functionality to store a parameter with a Color object as its value.
 class ColorSimParameter
          ColorSimParameter is a wrapper class for ColorParameter, to be used as a simulation parameter.
 class DoubleDataParameter
          DoubleDataParameter extends DataParameter to implement functionality to display a DoubleParameter within a GUI.
 class DoubleParameter
          DoubleParameter extends Parameter to implement functionality to store a parameter whose value is a double.
 class DoubleSimParameter
          DoubleSimParameter extends DoubleParameter to implement a DoubleParameter with minimum and maximum values.
 class IntDataParameter
          IntDataParameter is to be used to store a simulation parameter which is dynamic during running of the simulation.
 class IntParameter
          IntParameter extends Parameter to implement functionality to store an integer parameter.
 class IntSimParameter
          IntSimParameter extends Parameter to implement functionality to store an integer parameter.
